Another Q&A App

Documentation
-------------

The full documentation is at https://django-questions.readthedocs.org.

Quickstart
----------

Install django-questions::

    pip install django-questions

Then use it in a project::

    import questions

Features
--------

* TODO

Running Tests
--------------

Does the code actually work?

::

    source <YOURVIRTUALENV>/bin/activate
    (myenv) $ pip install -r requirements_test.txt
    (myenv) $ python runtests.py
